      <action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="S306">Mr. Menendez</sponsor> introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSCM00">Committee on Commerce, Science, and Transportation</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
